My life is exactly where I dreamed it to be not too long ago 

Moved cross country ✅ 
Moved to ACTUAL Tampa ✅ 
Opened my business downtown ✅ 
Made my own products @the_poshlounge ✅ 
Started therapy ✅ 
Become a better version of myself - in process 

There are so many goals I have left , are you guys down for the crazy journey I have planned for 30? 🫠 

To be completely raw, I don’t even know if half of this would’ve been possible if I hadn’t over dosed the beginning of the year. I honestly consider it to be a “rebirth” of who I NEED to be. I just remember writing while in the hospital of everything I wanted to do and how I would get there, the biggest part of it was releasing my past and understanding it had no place with me any more . 

If your history is haunting you, remember you are in control to make the changes you need. Life is beautiful and it’s art, you can create the masterpiece you imagine as long as ur discipline and positive ❤️

World travel for 30 🌍✨ I will help better the world , one volunteer in each country at a time. 

#fyp #explore
